data.description: You'll love this beautifully renovated Central Arlington home! Highlights include a covered front porch, granite countertops in the kitchen and bathroom, an ample amount of cabinet and counter space in the kitchen, nicely sized bedrooms, a generously sized backyard and so much more! This home is also located less than 5 miles from the Arlington Entertainment District and is within close proximity to several major highways, shopping and restaurants! Don't miss out on this must-see home!
